item.title: How do i get into my router?
item.dc:creator: @Sick_of_Air Sick of Air
item.description:
@Sick_of_Air wrote:

If he’s trying to get into his router, I’m pretty sure he doesn’t want a Hamachi one since they are shit.

goblin, just type in your router’s IP in the URL address bar. If you don’t know you router’s IP, go to Start > Network Places > View Network Connections. Then right click on your Local Area Connections and click Status. Then open the Support tab at the top and there is your IP.
